{"data": [{"id": "4745441", "title": "Enerpac Tool Group Stock Takes A Dive On Q1 Earnings", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Labourers Planning on Site\" data-id=\"1917054502\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">FatCamera</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>December 18th was a rough day for shareholders of <b>Enerpac Tool Group Corp.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EPAC\" title=\"Enerpac Tool Group Corp.\">EPAC</a></span>). As the broader market plunged following <a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2024/12/18/nx-s1-5230508/federal-reserve-interest-rates-economy-inflation\" rel=\"nofollow\">news</a> that the Federal Reserve would likely only be cutting interest rates twice next year</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745441-enerpac-tool-group-stock-takes-a-dive-on-q1-earnings", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 01:26:46"}, {"id": "4745440", "title": "Dividend Growers Hedge Against Trump Bump To Inflation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money growth\" data-id=\"1445810162\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1055px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>By Michael Clarfeld, CFA</p> <p>Portfolio Manager, ClearBridge Investments</p> <h2>There Will Be Second-Order Effects to Trump 2.0</h2> <p>Trump won \u2014 buy crypto! Trump won \u2014 buy energy stocks! Trump won and will loosen regulations on financial companies \u2014 buy bank stocks!</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745440-dividend-growers-hedge-against-trump-bump-to-inflation", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 01:07:31"}, {"id": "4745444", "title": "The GEO Group: Can Benefit On Trump's Mass Deportation Plan, But Stock Is Overvalued", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Prison\" data-id=\"117559713\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3426px\" height=\"2208px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Alex Potemkin</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Donald Trump is widely known to be in favor of tightening U.S. immigration policies. According to <a href=\"https://time.com/7171654/donald-trump-immigration-plan-2024/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">TIME</a>, Trump intends to commence mass deportations of millions of people, a project that could be marked by widespread workplace raids and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/117559713/image_117559713.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745444-geo-group-can-benefit-trumps-mass-deportation-plan-stock-overvalued", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 01:03:47"}, {"id": "4744998", "title": "Strategically Building A $100,000 Dividend Portfolio, With Altria As Your Core Holding", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458110161/image_458110161.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Package of Marlboro Red Label Filter Cigarettes\" data-id=\"458110161\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6048px\" height=\"4032px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458110161/image_458110161.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458110161/image_458110161.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458110161/image_458110161.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458110161/image_458110161.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458110161/image_458110161.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458110161/image_458110161.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458110161/image_458110161.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458110161/image_458110161.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">bmcent1</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Investment Thesis</strong></h2> <p>Portfolio allocation is a crucial factor that determines performance over the long term. This article will show you how to build a $100,000 dividend portfolio using 2 ETFs and 10 dividend paying companies, from which Altria (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458110161/image_458110161.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4744998-altria-stock-your-core-holding-strategically-building-100000-dividend-portfolio", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 01:00:00"}, {"id": "4745435", "title": "Hims & Hers: FDA Ruling May Close Compounded GLP-1 Drug 'Loophole', It Was Fun While It Lasted", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1193127525/image_1193127525.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A pair of scissors cutting a balloon string to release the balloon\" data-id=\"1193127525\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1193127525/image_1193127525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1193127525/image_1193127525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1193127525/image_1193127525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1193127525/image_1193127525.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1193127525/image_1193127525.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1193127525/image_1193127525.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1193127525/image_1193127525.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1193127525/image_1193127525.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h3>Investment Overview - Hims &amp; Hers Dealt Blow By FDA Decision - Background</h3> <p>I gave the stock of Hims &amp; Hers Health (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HIMS\" title=\"Hims &amp; Hers Health, Inc.\">HIMS</a></span>) a \"Buy\" rating in May this year, after the digital healthcare platform operator <a href=\"https://investors.hims.com/news/news-details/2024/Hims--Hers-Announces-Access-to-GLP-1-Injections-Passing-Cost-Savings-Onto-Customers/default.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://investors.hims.com/news/news-details/2024/Hims--Hers-Announces-Access-to-GLP-1-Injections-Passing-Cost-Savings-Onto-Customers/default.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">announced</a> it</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1193127525/image_1193127525.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745435-hims-and-hers-fda-ruling-may-close-compounded-glp-1-drug-loophole-it-was-fun-while-it-lasted", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 00:42:28"}, {"id": "4745433", "title": "Exxon Mobil: A Solid Prospect With Market-Beating Potential", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458995021/image_458995021.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"ExxonMobil\" data-id=\"458995021\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1229px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458995021/image_458995021.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458995021/image_458995021.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458995021/image_458995021.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458995021/image_458995021.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458995021/image_458995021.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458995021/image_458995021.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458995021/image_458995021.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458995021/image_458995021.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Lanier</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>With a market capitalization as of this writing of $491.5 billion, <b>Exxon Mobil Corporation</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XOM\" title=\"Exxon Mobil Corporation\">XOM</a></span>) is a true behemoth in the fossil fuel industry. The company touches on multiple parts of the energy space, not only when it</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458995021/image_458995021.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745433-exxon-mobil-a-solid-prospect-with-market-beating-potential", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 00:29:39"}, {"id": "4745431", "title": "Amer Sports: Expensive No Matter How You Slice It (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150131664/image_2150131664.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='customers shopping at large Arc\"teryx retail store' data-id=\"2150131664\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150131664/image_2150131664.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150131664/image_2150131664.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150131664/image_2150131664.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150131664/image_2150131664.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150131664/image_2150131664.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150131664/image_2150131664.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150131664/image_2150131664.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150131664/image_2150131664.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Robert Way</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p>Amer Sports (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AS\" title=\"Amer Sports, Inc.\">AS</a></span>) owns a portfolio of growing brands in the sports and outdoor market. It's most valuable brand, Arc'teryx, has seen impressive growth and, along with Salomon, has been contributing significantly to top-line growth and bottom-line margin expansion. In this article, I'll provide a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150131664/image_2150131664.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745431-amer-sports-expensive-no-matter-how-you-slice-it-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 00:24:08"}, {"id": "4745430", "title": "DGRO: It Just Doesn't Make Sense To Exclude Growth Stocks", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money growth - US paper currency\" data-id=\"1445810148\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1034px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810148/image_1445810148.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px